Package: xslt
Version: 1.0
Title: XSLT 1.0 Transformations
Description: An extension for the 'xml2' package to transform XML documents
    by applying an XSL stylesheet.
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen@berkeley.edu>
URL: https://github.com/ropensci/xslt
BugReports: https://github.com/ropensci/xslt/issues
Depends: xml2 (>= 1.1.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, xml2
SystemRequirements: libxslt: libxslt1-dev (deb), libxslt-devel (rpm)
License: GPL (>= 2)
